  Goa2 m7-bian2 koh thiah, phah-sng3 tai7-ke i2-keng beng5-pek8 liau2. Tai7-ke , teng2-bin7 e5 phi3-ju7 na7 si7 bo5 m7-tioh8 , lan2 e5 ki3-tit hit e5 lang5 chiu7-si7 phi3-ju7 cho3 Sin5 , hit ku3-oe7 phi3-ju7 cho3 lang5 lah. Oe7 e7 thang kap lang5 ti7-teh, chiu7-si7 i3-bi7 lang5 e7 thang kap Sin5 cho3-hoe2 e5 i3-su3. An2-ni hit e5 lang5 chiu7-si7 tit-tioh8 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 . Tioh8 chit-khoan2 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 chiah si7 chin e5 oah8-mia7 lah. 
  4. Eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah tit e7 tioh8
  In-ui7 ai3 hou7 lan2 ti7-chia beh lun7 e5 tai7-chi3 khah e7 beng5, lan2 boh8-tit hiam5 hui3-khi3, chiong lan2 sou2 kong2 liau2--e5, ti7-chia koh lai5 hoan chit8-pian3 . Lan2 ti7 pun2-hang7 e5 te7-ji7 tiau5 u7 mng7 chit8-ku3, kong2, ¡§Tau3-ti2 chaiN2-iuN7 chiah si7 oah8?¡¨ Tui3 chit ku3 lan2 i2-keng u7 in3 si3-ku3. Te7-it: tioh8 u7 pian3-oaN7, u7 chin3-pou7 . Te7-ji7 :tioh8 e7 thang chhut ti7 ka-ti7 e5 sim lai5 oah8-tang7. Te7-saN: tioh8 u7 sim-khiau3. Te7-si3: tioh8 u7 hap8 ti7 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7. 
  Chai7 goa2 e5 gu5-kian3, chiu7-si7 jin7 chit si3-tiau5 cho3 oah8-mia7 e5 phiau-chun2 goan5-chek. Thong chit thiN-kha-e7 e5 oah8-mia7 u7 chiong2-chiong2 , u7 khah koan5--e5, ia7 u7 khah ke7--e5; che long2 e7 thang iong7 chit si3-tiau5 goan5-chek lai5 hun-piat8. Chhiu7-bak8, hoe-chhau2(chiu7-si7 sit8-but8 ) e5 oah8-mia7 si7 kin7-kin7 hap8 ti7 te7-it tiau5 e5 goan5-chek; khim5-siu3 , hi5, thang5, hit teng2-lui7 (chiu7-si7 tong7-but8)e5 oah8-mia7 si7 hap8 ti7 te7-it, te7-ji7 , nng7-tiau5 e5 goan5-chek; chhin-chhiuN7 kau5 chit-lui7, sui-jian5 ia7-si7 siok8 ti7 tong7-but8, chiau3 lan2 sou2 khoaN3 i e5 oah8-mia7, pi2 pat8-hang7 tong7-but8 na2-chun2 u7 khah koan5 e5 khoan2, in-ui7 i tam7-poh8 ia7 u7 hap8 ti7 te7-saN tiau5 e5 goan5-chek. 
  Kau3 lan2 lang5, te7-it, te7-ji7, te7-saN, chit saN-tiau5 e5 goan5-chek chiu7 long2 u7 hap8; chong2-si7 chit cheng2 si7 peng5-siong5 lang5, pi2 peng5-siong5 lang5 khah kang3 chit8-kip, chiu7-si7 khah bo5 hap8 ti7 te7-saN e5 goan5-chek. Chit khoan2 lang5 , si7 hou7 lang5 kio3-cho3 cheng-seN, in-ui7 i li7 tong7-but8 bo5 loa7-hng7. Iah8 lang5 na7-si7 m7-na7 u7 hah8 ti7 te7-it, te7-ji7, te7-saN e5 goan5-chek, ia7-si7 u7 hah8 ti7 te7-si3 e5 goan5-chek; chit ho7 chiu7 m7-si7 peng5-siong5 lang5, chiu7-si7 seng3-jin5 gi7-su7 ; chit teng2 lang5 chiu7-si7 kap Sin5 peN5-peN5 tiam3. Peng5-siong5 lang5 eng2-eng2 ai3 pai3 chit ho7 lang5 cho3 Sin5. Che khiok si7 u7 chho3-gou7, na7-si7 chheng i cho3 Sin5 e5 kiaN2 , chiu7 bo5 m7-tioh8 . E7 thang cho3 kau3 Sin5 e5 kiaN2 , chiu7-si7 oah8-mia7 chin3-pou7 e5 kek8-kham2, cho3 lang5 it-seng e5 bok8-tek, chiu7-si7 chai7 ti-chia. 
  TaN tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 cho3, chiah e7 hap8 ti7 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7? Tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7 cho3, eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 chiah tit e7 tioh8? Tai7-ke choan-sim koh lai5 siuN7. 
  Eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 si7 sim2-mih8, lan2 i2-keng beng5-pek8 liau2; iah8 beh tit chit e5 oah8-mia7 u7 bang7 bo5, lan2 ia7 i2-keng chai. Chong2-si7 beh chaiN2-iuN7 tit, chaiN2-iuN7 cho3? Chhin-chhiuN7 Chin5-si2-hong5 e5 khoan2 , sai2 lang5 iong7 chiN5 be2 e7-tioh8 be7? Toan3-toan3 be7, toan3-toan3 bo5 bang7 lah. Lan2 e7 ki3-tit eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7, chiu7-si7 bo5 han7-liong7 e5 oah8-mia7, si7 be7 sai2-tit iong7 sim2-mih8 thang ka7 i che3-han7, ia7-si7 be7 sai2-tit iong7 sim2-mih8 thang ka7 i chhek-liong7. Na7-si7 e7 thang iong7 ni5-goeh8 thang ka7 i chhek-liong7 , khoaN3 si7 tng5 a2-si7 te2, hek8-si7 iong7 seng-khu ka7 i che3-han7, khoaN3 si7 li2-e5 goa2-e5 , a2-si7 pat8-lang5 e5 ; hit khoan2 chiu7 m7-si7 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7. 
  Koh-chai3 lan2 u7 chai, eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 si7 be7 iong7-tit hou7 sim2-mih8 thang ka7 i thiN chit8-hun, kiam2 chit8-ho5 , i si7 i ka-ti7 . M7-na7 an2-ni, i si7 ban7-hang7 e5 goan5-thau5 , si7 it-chhe3 u7 han7-liong7 e5 oah8-mia7 e5 thau5; m7-ku2 lan2 m7-si7 lan2 ka-ti7 , lan2 si7 tui3 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 chhut, lan2 e5 it-chhe3 si7 siu7 i chiang2-koan2. 
  Lang5 pi2 tong7-but8 khah chhut-sek e5 tiam2 chiu7-si7 u7 sim-khiau3. Lang5 e5 sim-khiau3 sou2 oah8-tang7 e5 sou2-chai7 , chiu7-si7 hun-piat8 chin ke2 (ti3-sek e5 sim), ho2-phaiN2 (to7-tek e5 sim), sui2-bai2 (ge7-sut8 e5 sim), chit saN hong-bin7. Chong2-si7 sim2-mih8 si7 chin neh? Sim2-mih8 si7 ho2 neh? Iah8 sim2-mih8 si7 sui2 neh? Chit saN hang7 si7 tui3 to2-loh8-lai5? Si7 lang5 ka-ti7 liap-cho7--e5 a2 m7-si7? Toan3-toan3 m7-si7. Chit saN-hang7 kap thiN-te7-kan it-chhe3 e5 su7-but8 sio-siang7 khoan2, long2 si7 tui3 ti7 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 chhut-lai5--e5. Chit saN-hang7 chiu7-si7 Sin5 e5 sim-su lah. 
  Lang5 e5 sim-khiau3 chit8-chong7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 kiaN3 . Chit saN-hang7 chin--e5, ho2--e5, sui2--e5, tui3 Sin5 hoat--chhut-lai5. Lang5 e5 sim-kiaN3 na7 u7 hiong3 hia khi3, chiu7 e7 kiat i e5 heng5-chong7 ti7 lang5 e5 sim-kiaN3 lai7 ; lang5 tui3 an2-ni u7 kam2-kak, chiah e7-hiau2 hun chin-ke2, piat8 sian7-ok, keng2 sui2-bai2. Lang5 e5 sim-khiau3 e7-hiau2 hun-piat8 chin-ke2, sian7-ok, sui2-bai2, hit e5 lang5 chiu7-si7 kio3-cho3 u7 jin5-keh. 
  HiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7 , lan2 lun7-kau3 chia , beh tit-tioh8 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 e5 lou7-keng3 khi2 m7-si7 beng5-pek8 liau2 mah? Chiu7-si7 an2-ni lah: lang5 tioh8 eng7 i e5 jin5-keh cho3 ki-chhou2 , bo5 siu7 it-chhe3 e5 khu-sok, thoat-li7 long2-chong2 e5 che3-han7, bo5 phau7 pat8-cheng2 e5 sim-su. Kan-ta hi-bong7 seng5-chiu7 Sin5 e5 i3, piau2-hian7 sin5 e5 to7, chin-sim chin7-lat8 bo5 hioh-khun3 cho3 sin5 e5 kang, kau3 khui3-tng7 chiah pang3-soah. Liat8-ui7, chit kui2-ku3 oe7 sui-si7 kan2-tan peng5-siong5 peng5-siong5 , chong2-si7 chit kui2-ku3 sit8-chai7 chiu7-si7 lang5 e5 liong5-sim e5 kiat-chiN , beh tit-tioh8 chin e5 oah8-mia7 e5 pi3-koat. Lan2 na7-si7 khak-sit8 tui3 ti7 lan2 e5 sim-koaN-te2 u7 sin3 chit kui2-ku3 si7 beh chhoa7 lang5 chin3-jip8 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 , chiong5-kim i2-au7 koat-sim hoaN-hi2 chiau3 an2-ni cho3. Chit-khoan2 lang5 siat-su2 si7 chu7 chit-tiap8 si2, ia7 si7 i2-keng jip8 ti7 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7, i e5 sim tiaN7-tioh8 u7 be7 kong2-tit e5 ho5-lok8. 
  Lan2 e7 ki3-tit Khong2-chu2 u7 kong2 , ¡¨Tiau bun5-to7 sek su2 kho2--i3 .¡¨ Chiu7-si7 kong2, lang5 na7-si7 cha2-khi2-si5 e7 thang tit-tioh8 to7-li2, seng5-chiu7 jin5-keh, e7-pou-si5 lai5 si2 , ia7 si7 thang. Chit-ku3 oe7 chiu7-si7 kap lan2 sou2-kong2 e5 siang7 i3-su3. Eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7 m7-si7 hit ho7 ai3 ka-ti7 put-si5 bak8-chiu kim-kim, tng5 hoe3-siu7 e5 lang5 sou2 tit e7-tioh8 , chiu7 tioh8 chin7-sim chin7-lat8 cho3 Sin5 e5 kang e5 lang5 chiah u7 hun7. 
  5. Hian7-kim e5 Tai5-oan5 si7 Oah8 a2-si7 si2
  ChaiN2-iuN7 chiah si7 oah8? chit e5 bun7-te5 thang kong2 lan2 i2-keng tai7-liok8 soat-beng5 liau2. SeN e5 lou7 na7-si7 ki3-jian5 chai, si2 e5 lou7 chiu7-si7 hit-e5 e5 to3-peng2. Lan2 na7 chiong teng2-tiau5 sou2 kong2-beng5 hit si3 hang7 e5 goan5-li2 ki3-tiau5 ti7 lan2 e5 sim-lai7, lan2 ka-ti7 to bian2-kong2 , chiu7-si7 sia7-hoe7 cheng3-lang5 e5 si2-oah8 lan2 to phoaN3-toan3 e7 hun-beng5, e7 thang hoat-kian3 kai2-kiu3 e5 hong-hoat. 
  Hian7-si5 e5 Tai5-oan5 si7 si2 a2-si7 oah8? Chit e5 bun7-te5 pi2 lan2 chit8-lang5 chit8 ka-chok8 e5 si2-oah8 m7-chai ke toa7 u7 loa7-che7? Chong2-si7 goa2 ti7-chia tioh8 koh phoe-beng5 kong2 chit8-ku3, i2-au7 sou2 beh kong2--e5 si7 kin7-kin7 theh8 lan2 Pun2-to2-lang5 hong-bin7 e5 chai5-liau7 kong2; khiok m7-si7 kong2 chit-khoan2 e5 pe3-peng7 si7 kan-ta lan2 chiah u7. Koh-chai3 kan-ta Pun2-to2-lang5 hong-bin7 e5 chai5-liau7 ma7-si7 u7 chin-che7, goa2 si7 kin7-kin7 theh8 kui2-tiam2 khi2-lai5 kong2 na7-tiaN7. 
  Te7-it, ai3 kap lan2 liat8-ui7 tui3 Tai5-oan5 e5 hak8-bun7 hong-bin7 kiam2-tiam2 khoaN3. Hak8-bun7 si7 sim2-mih8? Tai7-liok8 thang kong2 , hak8-bun7 si7 beh chhian2-beng5 chin-li2 e5 heng5-ui5. Hak8-bun7 e5 bok8-tek si7 beh kiu5 chin-li2. Sou2-ai3 kiu5 e5 chin-li2 , na7-si7 kiu5 u7-tioh8, chhian2 u7 beng5, hit e5 hak8-bun7 i2-keng chiu7-si7 seng5-kong liau2. Chong2-si7 , liat8-ui7 , chai7 lan2 e5 tiong-kan kiam2 m7-si7 khoaN3 hak8-bun7 si7 beh kiu5 li7-ek e5 khah-che7, kiu5 hak8-bun7 si7 beh kiu5 cho3-koaN kiu5 than3-chiN5, sou2-i2 na7-si7 be7 thang cho3-koaN kap than3-chiN5 , iah8 chiu7 liah8-cho3 thak8-chheh si7 bo5 lou7-eng7. 
  Beng7 Hu-chu2 kiam2 m7-si7 i2-keng u7 kong2-liau2. I kong2 , ¡§Hak8-bun7 e5 bok8-tek , m7-si7 beh kiu5 pat8-mih8 , si7 kan-ta beh kiu5 lan2 sou2 phah-m7-kiN3 e5 sim-khiau3 to3-tng2-lai5.¡¨ Lan2 sou2 phah-m7-kiN3 e5 sim-khiau3 si7 siaN2-hoe3? Chiu7-si7 lan2 sim-koaN e5 kiaN3 u7 chhiuN7-sian, chin-li2 e5 iaN2 chio3 be7 beng5 ti7 lan2 e5 sim-lai7 e5 i3-su3. Iah8 lan2 oh8 hak8-bun7 chiu7-si7 beh chhit lan2 e5 sim-kiaN3 hou7 i beng5, hou7 chin-li2 e5 iaN2 chio3 e7 hian7 ti7 lan2 sim-lai7. Kho2-lin5; m7-ku2 phou2-thong lan2 teh khoaN3 hak8-bun7 m7-si7 an2-ni khoaN3. Khah-che7 liah8 hak8-bun7 chun2-cho3 beh tit li7-ek e5 hoat-tou7, ti3-kau3 lan2 e5 hak8-bun7 i2-keng kou-ta5 si2--khi3 chin-ku2, chin-ku2 lah! In-ui7 kong2 thak8-chheh si7 beh tit li7-ek , sou2-i2 na7 bo5 li7-ek thang tit chiu7 siuN7 kong2, m7-bian2 thak8! Lan2 e5 lang5 thak8-chheh--e5 chin-chio2, chiu7-si7 tui3 an2-ni lai5. 
  Koh-chai3, chin-li2 si7 chhiaN2 chit8 piN , li7-ek cho3 thau5-cheng5; sou2-i2 tai7-khai3 e5 lang5 to si7 ko2-chhiaN2 hou5-tou5. Long2 si7 khioh kou2-cha2 lang5 e5 chau-phoh, m7-kaN2 chhut-lat8 sin-khui pat8-tiau5 e5 ho2-lou7 , hoat-beng5 khah-chhim e5 chin-li2. Sou2-i2 na7 kong2 thak8-chheh, chiu7-si7 Su3-su , Ngou2-keng, Kou2-bun5;long2 si7 kui2-na7 chheng-ni5 e5 hoe3-te2. Hit kui2-pun2 chheh, m7-na7 chheh-phoe5 ju2-ju2 kau3 iuN5-kou5-kou5, lai7-bin7 e5 ji7 ia7 i2-keng hou7 cheng3-lang5 e5 chhiu2-sioh8 kou5 kau3 beh bo5 beng5 khi3. Lan2 kong2 pian3-oaN7 chin3-pou7 si7 oah8-mia7 te7-it e5 tiau5-kiaN7. Li2 khoaN3 , lan2 e5 hak8-bun7 si7 kin7-kin7 han7-tiaN7 ti7 hit kui2-pun2 chheh, oah8-mia7 ti7 to2-loh8 neh? M7-na7 an2-ni, iau2-ku2 u7 chin-che7 e5 siau2-jin5, m7-na7 i bo5 khoaN3 chin-li2 tang7, bo5 beh chhut-lat8 khi3 kiu5 sin, chiu7-si7 cheng5 e5 gau5-lang5 khou2-sim sou2 hoat-beng5--e5, i to m7 seng5-sim siu2, hoan2-tng2 ui7-tioh8 chit8-si5 ka-ti7 e5 li7-ek, chiong tit8-tit8 e5 chin-li2 au2-cho3 kui2-na7 chat, cho3 i koe3-kio5 e5 koaiN2-a2. Ai5--ah! Tai5-oan5 e5 hak8-bun7 si7 si2 a2-si7 oah8? 
  Te7-ji7 , chhiaN2 kap tai7-ke lai5 siuN7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 chong-kau3. Lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 chong-kau3 si7 oah8 a2-si7 si2? Liat8-ui7 chhi3-siuN7 khoaN3. Lan2 tong5-pau e5 tiong-kan bong7 Put8-kau3 e5 ia7 u7, hong7 To7-kau3 e5 ia7 u7 , hong7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 ia7 u7; pai3 chiong2-chiong2 e5 chap8-chhui3-sin5 ia7 si7 u7; koh-chai3 liah8 Khong2-chu2 cho3 Sin5 ti7-teh pai3 e5 ia7 si7 u7; su7 ka-ti7 e5 chou2-sian e5 sin5-chu2 teh pai3--e5 ia7 si7 u7. Siok8-gu2 kong2, ¡§Cheng5-li2 u7 chit8, si7 bo5 nng7.¡¨ Chiah-che7 hang7 chong-kau3 e5 tiong-kan tek-khak u7 tioh8--e5, ia7 u7 m7-tioh8--e5. Tioh8 m7-tioh8, lan2 ti7-chia chhiaN2 mai3-tit lun7; lan2 chhiaN2 chiau3 kok-lang5 sou2 sin3-e5 , long2 ka7 i jin7-cho3 tioh8. Lan2 sou2 ai3 lun7--e5, chiu7-si7 koh-lang5 sou2-sin3 e5 chong-kau3 si7 oah8 a2-si7 si2? 
  Chhi3-siuN7-khoaN3 , sim2-mih8 si7 chong-kau3? Lan2 na7 hian ji7-tian2 khi2-lai5 khoaN3, chiu7 chai-iaN2 ¡§Chong¡¨ si7 ¡§Chu2¡¨ e5 i3-su3, iah8 ¡§Chu2¡¨ chiu7-si7 choan chu2 chit8-hang7 e5 i3-su3. ¡§Kau3¡¨ chiu7-si7 ka3-si7 e5 i3-su3. Sou2-i2 thang chai ¡§Chong-kau3¡¨ nng7-ji7 hap8 cho3-hoe2 e5 i3-su3, chiu7-si7 ¡§Choan-chu2 chit8-hang7 e5 ka3-si7.¡¨ Kong2 chit8 ku3 khah-beng5, Chong-kau3 chiu7-si7 lang5 choan-sim khian5-seng5 keng3-pai3 Sin5 , the2-liong7 Sin5 e5 i3-su3, hian3 ka-ti7 chit8 sin siu2 Sin5 e5 ka3-si7, cho3 Sin5 e5 su7-giap8. E7-tit chiau3 an2-ni cho3, ka-ti7 e5 sim-koaN-te2 long2 bo5 hun-ho5 e5 gi5-ga7, chiong choan-sim choan5-mia7 long2 kau-tai7 hou7 Sin5 chiang2-koan2, chit8-sut-a2 to m7-kaN2 theh8-chhut ka-ti7 e5 su-sim. Tui3 an2-ni chu7-jian5 chiu7 e7 seN-chhut chin toa7 e5 peng5-an. Chit khoan2 e5 chong-kau3 , chiah si7 u7 oah8-mia7 e5 chong-kau3. 
  Chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 sou2-u7 che7-che7 hang7 e5 chong-kau3, lau2-sit8 kong2, tui3 kin-te2 i2-keng chiu7 chho3-gou7--e5 si7 chin-che7, chiu7-si7 i sou2 keng3-pai3 e5 Sin5 m7-tioh8 e5 u7 chin-che7. Chit-hang7 chiau3-sit8 tioh8 ai3 gi7-lun7 chin, in-ui7 kiaN-cho3 gi7-lun7 liau2 siuN khoah, tian-to3 khah m7-ho2, sou2-i2 chiau3 teng2-bin7 e5 iok-sok chit-tiam2 chhiaN2 mai3 kong2, Lan2 kan-ta lai5 khoaN3 teh pai3 e5 lang5, pai3 liau2 sim2-mih8 khoan2 , si7 oah8 e5 pai3-hoat, a2-si7 si2 e5 pai3-hoat? 
  Te7-it, pai3 e5 lang5 bo5-beng5 i sou2 pai3 e5 Sin5 si7 sim2-mih8. ChaiN2-iuN7 i thai3 tioh8 keng3-pai3 hit e5 Sin5, pai3 e5 lang5 kap Sin5 si7 u7 sim2-mih8 koan-he7 . Pai3 e5 lang5 chit-tiam2 long2 bo5 beng5-pek8 si7 khah-che7; put-ko3 si7 kan-ta thiaN-kiN3 lang5 kong2 Koan-im khah u7 siaN3, chiu7 pai3 Koan-im; thiaN-kiN3 Ma2-chou2 khah u7 siaN3, chiu7 pai3 Ma2-chou2; ThiaN-kiN3 tioh8 he7 Seng5-hong5 , chiu7 pai3 Seng5-hong5. Na7 kong2 si7 hoan7-tioh8 to2 chit8-hng e5 Ong5-ia5 iah8 chiu7 khi2-lang5 khi2-be2 beh chhiaN2 Ong5-ia5 , kan-ta loan7-pai3 chit8-tiuN5. Hit sian Sin5 e5 chi2-i3 si7 ti7 to2-loh8, pai3 e5 lang5 long2 bo5 the2-thiap, long2 bo5 ti3-i3 beh chun-siu2. 
  Ka-ti7 cho3-ho2 a2-si7 cho3-phaiN2 , u7 choe7 a2-si7 bo5 choe7 , e7 kham-ti Sin5 e5 ai3-sioh po2-hou7 a2-si7 be7, long2 bo5 siuN7 ; kin7-kin7 siuN7 cho3 u7 sio-kim chiu7 tek-khak u7 po2-pi3, loan7-loan7 pai3 , loan7-loan7 kiu5, chiu7-si7. Sio chit8-pah kim , tiam2 chit8-tui3 chek, chhah saN-ki hiuN; iah8 chiu7 beh kiu5 seN-kiaN2, seN-sun, choan5-ke peng5-an tng5 hoe3-siu7. 
  U7-e5 he7 kong2 , Chit-tu3 chiN5 na7 po2-pi3 than3 koe3-chhiu2 , chiu7 beh cho3 hi3 lai5 sia7; khah hiong-thai2--e5, ia7 u7 he7; na7 e7 poah8 iaN5-kiau2 , chiu7 beh thai5-ti tou5-iuN5 lai5 keng3-hian3. Siat-su2 ti7 Sin5 e5 bin7-cheng5 teh he7 hiah e5 oe7, mai3-tit tiam3 ti7 chhu3-lai7 liam7, na7 khui-siaN kong2 beng5-beng5 hou7 lang5 thiaN , ka-ti7 be7 siuN7 kian3-siau3 e5 lang5 , m7-chai u7 kui2-e5! Chit-khoan2 kiam2 m7-si7 liah8 Sin5 chun2-cho3 chiah8-chiN5-koaN teh khoan2-thai7 mah? 
  Ui7-tioh8 ka-ti7 e5 li7-ek tui3 Sin5 teh keng3-hian3, kap phaiN2 peh-seN3 teh siap ak koaN-li7 e5 au7-chhiu2 u7 sim2-mih8 cheng-chha? Chit-khoan2 e5 sim-li2 kiat-kiok8 si7 si2 a2-si7 oah8, goan7 lan2 chhim-chhim ai3 seng2-chhat! Koh chhiaN2 tai7-ke lai5 khoaN3 hoe5-siuN7 , to7-su7 , tang5-ki , ang-i5 e5 sou2-kiaN5 sou2-cho3 si7 chaiN2-iuN7? 
  Chiah e5 lang5 si7 ti7 Sin5 kap lang5 e5 tiong-kan, chit8-peng5 the3 Sin5 thoan5 chi2-i3, chit8-peng5 the3 lang5 hok8-sai7 Sin5, piau2-beng5 lang5 e5 sim-goan7, hou7 lang5 e7 thang khah-khoai3 chiap-kin7 Sin5. Sou2-i2 chit ho7 su7 chiu7 tioh8 chin-chiaN3 chheng-khi3 u7 tek-heng7 e5 lang5 chiah e7 kham-tit tng. Sek-khia, Ia5-sou, chiu7-si7 chit khoan2 lang5 e5 choe3 li2-siong2 , choe3 ho2 e5 bou7-hoan7. Sek-khia ui7-tioh8 ai3 chin7 i e5 pun2-hun7, ong5-kiong m7-kaN2 toa3, hong5-te3-ui7 m7-kaN2 che7, lak8-chap8 goa7 ni5 e5 tiong-kan siu7-liau2 bo5-han7 e5 hong-song, kiaN5-soa2 pian3 thiN-kha-e7 soeh-beng5 kiu3-khou2 kiu3-lan7 e5 chin-li2. Na7 lun7 Ia5-sou e5 it-seng, si7 iau2-ku2 khah hou7 lan2 thang kam2-kek, I ui7-tioh8 beh thoan5 ThiN e5 chi2-i3 , ai3 kiu3 choan5-jin5-lui7 put-lun7 sim2-mih8 kok e5 lang5 chhut choe7-ok, jit8-jit8 kiaN5 ho2-su7, pang-chan7 kan-khou2 lang5. Lang5 u7 oan3-hin7 I, khun2-tiok8 I, I ia7 tek-khak bo5 hin7-lang5. Kau3 boe2 hou7 lang5 teng3-si2 ti7 Sip8-ji7-ke3 , hou7 lang5 iong7 chhiuN-to chhak8 heng-kham2; khui3-si beh tng7 e5 si5-chun7, I iau2-ku2 si7 m7-kaN2 be7-ki3-tit Sin5, iau2-ku2 si7 the3 lang5 kiu5 sia3-choe7, iau2-ku2 si7 choan-sim kiaN5 jin5-ai3. Chong2-si7 hian7-si5 chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 hoe5-siuN7 , to7-su7 , chit cheng2-lui7 e5 lang5 sou2 cho3 sim2-mih8 khoan2 , bian2 kong2 hou7 lan2 chin thang siong-sim thou2 toa7-khui3, chiu7-si7 Ki-tok kau3-hoe7 e5 thoan5-to7 sian-seN khah-che7 e5 sou2-cho3 si7 sim2-mih8 iuN7? Hoe5-siuN7 kap to7-su7 khiok si7 kap in be7 pi2-tit, m7-ku2 in e5 chhui3-lai7 sou2 liam7 e5 keng-bun5 kap in e5 kha-chhiu2 sou2 cho3 chhut-lai5 e5 su7-chek, pi2-kau3 khoaN3 si7 chaiN2-iuN7 khah che7? In sou2-kong2 kap sou2-cho3 e5 kiam2 m7-si7 toa7-toa7 bo5 sio-siang7? 
  Ai5--ah! Chit cheng2-lui7 e5 kang sit8-chai7 si7 se3-kan choe3 toa7 e5 thian-chit. Kho2-lin5! Chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 soa3 chha-put-to si7 pian3-chiaN5 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8 hang7 than3-chiN5 e5 seng-li2. 
  Chit-phiN i2-keng lun7 thai3-tng5 liau2, phah-sng3 m7-bian2 koh kong2 sim2-mih8, liat8-ui7 ia7 i2-keng kau3-giah8 beng5-pek8 liau2. Chong2-si7 chhiaN2 koh hou7 goa2 kong2 chit8-ku3 cho3 chit-phiN e5 chong2-kiat. Goa2 kong2 , kin-a2-jit8 e5 Tai5-oan5 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-phian3 e5 thiong2-pou. Thiong2-pou! Thiong2-pou si7 siaN2 sou2-chai7? Thiong2-pou chiu7-si7 si2-khut lah, chiu7-si7 bo5 oah8-mia7 e5 sou2-chai7. Liat8-ui7 e5 tiong-kan kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 beh me7 goa2 kong2 siau2-oe7! Goa2 m7-si7 kong2 siau2-oe7 , si7 kong2 sit8-chai7. ChhiaN2 thiaN goa2 hun-thiah. 
  Liat8-ui7 , thiong2-pou sou2 u7-e5 si7 sim2-mih8? Bong7! Kut-thau5! Teh noa7 e5 sin-si! Chiah-e5 i2-goa7 iau2-u7 sim2-mih8 bo5? U7, ia7 u7 chheN-chhau2 ti7-teh io5-hong, thang5 ti7-teh chhia, choa5 ti7-teh so5, kau2 ti7-teh phiN7, lai7-hioh8 ti7-teh khou, teh seh8 . I2-goa7 na7-si7 iau2-u7 chiu7-si7 kui2-e5-a2 in2-hun5 tham3-bong7 chhi-chham2 e5 lang5 na7-tiaN7. Chai7 thiong2-pou si7 bo5 u7 oah8-mia7 lah, bo5 u7 oah8-tang7 khoai3-lok8 nga2-ti3 sun5-kiat e5 oah8-mia7, kan-ta si7 peh8-kut si2-si hoe3-bong7 pian3-pian3 moa2-moa2 si7. Chong2-kong2 , thiong2-pou si7 u7-heng5 bo5-mia7 e5 sou2-chai7. 
  Goa2 kong2 hian7-si5 lan2 Tai5-oan5 kho2-pi2 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-phian3 e5 thiong2-pou . chiu7-si7 ai3 kong2 chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 hian7-si5 kan-ta u7 heng5-sek bo5 cheng-sin5 e5 i3-su3. Tai7-ke na7 liah8-chin kiam2-tiam2 khoaN3 , phah-sng3 tek-khak e7 kap goa2 tong5-kam2. Goa2 koh chhi3 ki2 chit8-nng7 hang7 cheng3-beng5 khoaN3. Liat8-ui7 chhiaN2 khoaN3 lan2 e5 hi3. Lun7 cho3-hi3 khiok toa7 pou7-hun7 si7 beh hou7 lang5 khoaN3 hoaN-hi2, chong2-si7 hi3 e5 hau7-ko2 m7-na7 kan-ta an2-ni, hi3 e7 iong2 lang5 e5 seng3-cheng5, tiong2 lang5 e5 kian3-sek, si7 chit8-cheng2 sia7-hoe7 kau3-hoa3 e5 ki-koan. M7-ku2 , li2 khoaN3 , lan2 Tai5-oan5 hian7-si5 e5 hi3 si7 chaiN2-iuN7? Cho3-hi3 e5 lang5 ka-ti7 u7 kam2-kak chit8 e5 toa7 su2-beng7, bo5? Cho3-hi3--e5 u7 liau2-kai2 i sou2 cho3 tak8-chhut hi3 e5 iau3-tiam2 oah8-mia7, bo5? Bo5 lah! m7-na7 i be7-hiau2 che, chiu7-si7 i sou2 kong2 e5 khau2-peh8 sou2 chhiuN3 e5 khek-bun5, e7 beng5-pek8 e5 m7-chai u7 kui2 lang5? Chiu7-si7 khoaN3-hi3 e5 lang5 ia7 si7 chit8-iuN7 . PeN5-kha e5 lang5 kho2-pi2 ah-a2 teh thiaN lui5, peN5-teng2 iu7 oan2-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8 kun5 siau2-lang5 teh loan7-choh. Sou2 poaN e5 chhut-thau5 iu7 si7 chhian-phian it-lut8 choan5 bo5 pian3-oaN7 kap chin3-pou7, long2 si7 kui2-pah ni5 cheng5 e5 ku7 hoe3-sek. Koh-chai3 chhiaN2 thiaN lan2 e5 im-gak8 khoaN3, hian5-phou2 na7 m7-si7 ¡§Toa7 khui-mng5, ¡¨ chek-si7 ¡§Chiong-kun-leng7;¡¨ Pak-koan2 chiu7-si7 ¡§Thian-sui2-koan.¡¨ Ban7-hang7 to long2 si7 kap Han3-ioh8 siang7 chit8 khoan2 , long2 si7 chun-siu2 kou2-hoat che3-cho7--e5 , m7-na7 si7 ta-so3 bo5 bi7-sou3, ki5-sit8 long2 si7 seN-phu2 chhau3-sioh8 lah! 
  Liat8-ui7 hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7 ! goa2 m7-si7 ai3 loan7-kong2 , lau2-sit8 goa2 si7 bo5-ta5-oa5. Goa2 taN put-jim2 koh ke kong2, chi2 goan7 tai7-ke sio-kap toa7 koat-sim, gian2-kiu3 chu7-sin chin3-chhu2 e5 hong-hoat, boh8-tit ka-ti7 loe2-chi3, boh8-tit ban7-hang7 kan-ta sun5-kui to7-ki2 kiah8 hiuN toe3-pai3. Na7-si7 an2-ni tai7-ke beh chin3-pou7, e7 thang kap lang5 tang5-che7-khia7, tek-khak si7 bo5 loa7-ku2. Ai5--ah!Liat8-ui7 , lan2 na7 beh koh m7-si7 an2-ni cho3 , na7 koh m7 si5-si5 chu3-i3 ka-ti7 kai2-kek oaN7-sin, kan-ta gong7 siu2 chiong5-chian5 e5 hoat-tou7, chai chit-e5 jit8-jit8 teh chin3-pou7 e5 se3-kai3 , lan2 tek-khak tioh8 cho3 lang5 e5 boe2-au7 to2-teh hou7 lang5 thoa. Liat8-ui7 , lan2 e5 chou2-sian sou2 pang3 hou7 lan2 e5 bun5-beng5 ki-giap8 , sit8-chai7 si7 pi2 pat8-lang5 e5 u7 khah-sui2 khah-toa7. M7-ku2 chhut lan2 au7-tai7 chiah e5 put-siau3 kiaN2-sun kan-ta e7-hiau2 khun3, chiah8, che7; be7-hiau2 lo5-lek8 keng-eng5 hou7 i sui2 koh-khah sui2 , toa7 koh-khah toa7. Chit8-peng5 , lang5 si7 na2 kou-ta na2 ng5-sng; chit8-peng5 , ki-giap8 si7 na2 hong-hoe3 na2 phoa3-sng2, oan2-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 ho2-giap8-lang5 e5 liau2-boe2-kiaN2 . Lang5 kan-ta to2 tiam3 bin5-chhng5 teh lan2-si, toa7-chhu3 pang3 teh hou7 hong-soa eng, ti-tu keN-bang7 , chiau2-a2 choh-siu7, peh8-hia7 chhng2-khang; bo5 loa7-ku2 na7 m7-si7 toa7-chhu3 to2 loh8-lai5, ka7 i kham3-bat8-khi3, tek-khak ia7-si7 hou7 soaN-khim5 ia2-siu3 ka7 i thoa-khi3 chiah8. 
